Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全國大賽第6日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽場A第3回合的比賽目前進行到副將前半戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東四局一本場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莊家是愛宕絹惠選手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
